tip.text: We sit at the counter, the chef can speak a little bit English and he tried his best to communicate with us. Very friendly people around, and most importantly, the food was really impressive.

venue.name: Kagurazaka Ishikawa (神楽坂 石かわ)

tip.text: Booked 2 months in advance and luckily we got a table for two for lunch. Lunch comes with almost all the same dishes but the price is much more affordable. Amazing...
